node.text:
Success is NOT about waiting around, thinking positively, and then hopefully one day you’ll get it.

It’s about doing whatever it takes.

It’s about practicing it till you become it.

And it’s about ignoring the haters and following your heart.

How can you do that?

Ask yourself, “What would the successful version of me do?”

The habits… the decisions… the way you think… the words you say… the people you hang out with.

Write everything down on a piece of paper and then do that.

Even if you don’t know how.

Even if it scares you.

And even if you don’t have the right skills or knowledge, you learn them.

If you’re going to do what the successful version of you would do, put “I will be successful” in the comments.

node.text:
I know you might see opportunities online that could be perfect for you. 
 
But you don’t have the financial resources right now. 
 
What I’ve found in myself and my mentees, is… 
 
It’s the people that are the most resourceful that get the furthest in life. 
 
So, don’t just give up because you don't have the money. 
 
Find a way to get it. 
 
Exhaust all your options. 
 
Sell some old clothes or things around the house on eBay. 
 
Find free things online you can resell. 
 
See if you can find someone to lend you money. 
 
I know if you get creative you’ll find a way to make your dreams a reality. 
 
Comment below different ways you can be resourceful.

node.text:
If everything comes crashing down.

If you lost everything.

Would you be able to survive?

If the stock market crashed.

If a 3rd world war broke out.

Or even if you lost your job, would you survive?

Or would you go hungry?

Would your family go hungry?

You see, in life we can never predict outcomes.

We can only prepare for the worst and hope for the best.

That’s why it’s so important to have a high income skill.

Because a high income skill is a dependable way to continue making money, even if things go sideways.

I reveal my secrets about high income skills and making good money in my training courses. If you want to get all the details on that DM me. 

So let me ask you, are you committed to developing a high income skill so if things go sideways, you will stay safe?

Give me a “hell yea!” in the comments below.

He is a Haitian-American businessperson, a world-renowned public speaker, mentor, coach, and one of the most of influential leaders in the industry of network marketing. He is a multi-lingual marketing strategist who has countless years of solid and diverse professional experience in the areas of business development and leadership.

He has trained hundreds of thousands of people on how to build a successful network marketing business and has helped many people improve and strengthen their personal and leadership skills with his specialized mentorship training programs.

He has conducted many lectures at universities around the world to share his knowledge on how to better prepare for the future. He has received high academic recognition for his dedication and contribution to universities and their students.

Coach Legend’s success is due to incredible persistence, charisma and sincere desire to help people succeed. His laser-like focus, years of diligent work and ongoing self-development, along with total dedication have resulted in an evidenced strong leadership that delivered massive and excellent benefits to all ethnic groups, especially in his Haitian community.
